                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8739" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1340</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2539 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">知之易，行之难：数字化背景下铁骑力士预算管理实践的价值创造逻辑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Easier Known Than Done: The Value Creation Logic of Budget Management Practice in TECHLEX Group Under the Digitalization Background</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冯源，陈扬（通讯作者），王丽花，庞新月，林海芬，付嵘</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">铁骑力士食品有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全面预算管理；价值创造；数字化；全产业链企业；2024百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Comprehensive budget management; Value Creation; Digitalization;Full industry chain enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以农业产业化国家重点龙头企业——铁骑力士集团（简称“铁骑力士”）为研究对象，从该企业的创立和全产业链布局出发，以其全面预算管理体系建立的前因后果为线索，按照时间顺序，详细阐述了该企业在面临行业竞争激烈、全产业链经营管理难度高、资源配置效率低等众多压力的情况下，如何利用全面预算管理体系实现价值创造的全过程。本案例重点关注了铁骑力士围绕“打造全产业链，实现千亿营收”这一战略目标进行的全面预算管理实践。基于数字化系统，集团建立了目标分解、预算编制、预算控制、预算考核的全流程闭环体系，最终在2022年和2023年分别达到了降本5.8亿元和3.94亿元的巨大成效。通过本案例的学习和讨论，学员可以更好地理解全面预算管理对于企业战略落地以及价值创造的重要作用以及全产业链企业应该如何使用全面预算管理来控制成本、创造价值，进而增强自身竞争力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study takes TECHLEX Group (hereinafter referred to as “TECHLEX”), a leading national enterprise in agriculture industrialization, as the research object. Starting from the establishment and complete industry chain layout of the enterprise, it follows the causes and consequences of the establishment of Comprehensive budget management system as the clue, and chronologically elaborates the process of how the enterprise created value by comprehensive budget management system under the multiple pressures of fierce external industry competition, high management complexity in diversified operations, and inefficient resource allocation. This case study focuses on TECHLEX’s comprehensive budget management practices in pursuit of its strategic goal of “building a complete industry chain and achieving a revenue of hundreds of billions.” Based on its digital system, TECHLEX has established a closed-loop system covering target decomposition, budget formulation, budget control, and budget evaluation, and finally achieved significant cost reductions of 580 million and 394 million yuan in 2022 and 2023 respectively. Through the study and discussion of this case, students can better understand the vital role comprehensive budget management plays in realizing corporate strategies and value creation, and how diversified enterprises should utilize comprehensive budget management to control costs, generate value, and enhance their competitiveness.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》，《管理会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全面预算管理；预算编制；预算控制；预算考核</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
